Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:10.40,lrc,,0,0,0,,千古江山如诗如画
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:15.98,lrc,,0,0,0,,还我一个太平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:16.63,lrc,,0,0,0,,天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:21.63,lrc,,0,0,0,,下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你好糊涂啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你扣了刘备的粮饷也就罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你干吗还要扣孙将军的粮草军械
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙文台何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是盟军的先锋大将
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这些我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不但知道孙文台的战功
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还知道他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从来不把咱们袁盟主放在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然你已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你还得罪他做甚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 你就听愚弟一句话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}汉室气数已尽即将灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有愚者才傻乎乎的一味扶汉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恶者如董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早已篡汉自立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是许多袅雄想做而不敢做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是想叫我做愚者还是做恶者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既不做愚者也不做恶者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应当做智者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼下 虽然十八路诸侯会盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是十八路诸侯的真正动机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:04:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}未必是为国除贼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们只是想在天下破乱了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为自己寻得一块最大的地盘而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最可怕的是长沙太守孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚如果破洛阳斩董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他会不会把西凉兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}囊入自己的手中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.00,0:04:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他会不会坐镇朝廷 拥兵自立
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会不会取代董卓称霸天下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}成为比董卓更可怕的枭雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不是没有可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.43,0:04:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们的上策就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在剿灭董卓的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也大大削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚等诸侯的兵马势力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最好让他们一起灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下自然就落到袁氏的囊中了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.02,0:05:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这些我何尝不知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你做得也太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想 孙坚是盟军的先锋大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他一旦兵败
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}数十万盟军将土崩瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到时候你我都将身败名裂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还谈什么功名大业
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨夜三更李傕郭汜二将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}率领八万西凉精骑夜袭孙坚大营
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚折兵损将
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已退出白马要寨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓亲率二十五万西凉大军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倾城而出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}扬言要为国剿贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}五日内斩孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十日内取
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}取袁盟主首级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你听到了 我们倒成贼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真可谓是胜者为王 败者为贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果董卓胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的一切妙计
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都成了水中月 镜中花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这孙坚败得也太快了吧 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}愚蠢 害得我更愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚没有粮食能打仗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙文台兵败早在我预料之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹将军来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敢问孟德兄为何如此说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.61,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为孙坚虽然英勇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.01,0:06:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是求胜心切 孤军深入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已成骄兵 而骄兵必败
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敢问袁盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此时此刻你准备如何应变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}立即将孙文台败战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董贼亲征的军情传达至各部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之后召集各镇诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共商御敌大策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你万万不可将孙坚兵败的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.01,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉各诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相反 你要告诉大伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚胜了 而且是大胜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.62,0:07:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓才是兵败如山倒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在就等着大家伙一拥而上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}攻下虎牢关 直取洛阳城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}否则的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚兵败
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必然会引起各诸侯的惧敌之心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而人心一散 盟军就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}帅台设宴 为孙将军庆功
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}列位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙文台兄大破贼军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大长我盟军的声威
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等为孙将军遥相庆贺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为孙将军相贺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董贼弹指可灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等数日后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就可在京城把酒庆功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听说董卓已经拥兵出关了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此事确否
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么我等还要在此聚饮高会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}兵法云 以静制动 以逸待劳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乃胜战之道也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓的大军既已出关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙文台的孤军便处于险境了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}盟主就不担心他会兵败吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为何扣下我哥哥的粮饷不发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何还打我的属下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你一个小小的步弓手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎敢如此无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎的 俺张飞对这无耻之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}历来无礼 你们敢怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}列位诸公
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你们容得下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.53,0:09:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这三位在这里肆意放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就容我袁术告老还乡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公路兄息怒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁公路 位居副盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}掌管我十九路诸侯之粮饷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂能一走了之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你走了我们吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吃什么 是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}坐坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然如此 容我三兄弟告退
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德 留步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德 你乃汉皇宗亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}犹如我盟军大纛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂能一走了之
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你走了我等岂不寒心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德不必寒心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你完全知道 天下虽大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}列位却难以并列于世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前面那座城池
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那便是袁绍的大营
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凭我的赤兔马 方天戟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}视十八路诸侯如草芥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}待会儿交兵时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.05,0:11:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会亲手斩下袁绍的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以报义父厚恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我儿英雄盖世天下无敌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过 袁绍他也是徒有虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不足为虑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他的狗头可以暂寄于其项上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但有一个人的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉先务必替咱家把他取来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恶贼曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这小子咱家恨透他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恨不得把他碎尸万段
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挫骨扬灰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才能解我的心头之恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.83,0:12:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿臣一定会砍下曹操的头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你再看 看看前面那座城关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}极其高大坚固
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我西凉军骑善于野外作战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但不善于攻坚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果袁绍他据守不战的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可就颇为麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父有何意见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想啊 咱们这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让大军在此设伏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你带领百骑前去挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}设法把袁绍引出关来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们在野外和他决一雌雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无需百骑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.34,0:13:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}单骑便可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍这等势利之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他有什么资格做盟主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我走之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真应该扇他几个大耳刮子再走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟 收起你那大耳刮子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当心脏了自己的手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不瞒二位兄弟说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我其实并不想离开盟军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是他们不容我等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么着 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还惦记这十九镇将军的宝座
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}区区虚名何足留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是惦记着洛阳城内的蒙难天子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}盟军原本可以杀进京城灭贼兴汉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个好办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们三兄弟只管杀进洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}砍下董卓的脑袋就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟 就是莽撞 大哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们走了也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来时三兄弟 走时兄弟仨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无牵无挂 志在天下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍曹操 尔等听着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫要做缩头乌龟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快快出来和我吕布决一死战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军已杀到关前了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多少兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关前只有吕布一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他单人闯关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}指名要取曹操头颅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多谢多谢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某又要扬名天下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}列位将军 区区吕布只身闯关
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}视众将军如无物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是可忍孰不可忍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我部悍将刘三刀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三刀之内必斩吕布于马下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有上将韩勇可出战吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二位且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有北海勇将王冲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他早就想刀劈吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夺下赤兔马做他自己的坐骑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}韩将军 刘将军 王将军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经出城 与吕布战到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三个回合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三位将军全都被吕布斩落马下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传令 紧闭城门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}任何人不得擅自出战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关内各镇诸侯听着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们胆小如鼠 缩首如龟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看我吕布如何教训你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他真狂妄 他要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}关内诸侯们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们不是有十八镇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日就让我吕布来送你们十八箭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们怕和我单独交战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就统统滚出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}十八镇诸侯一起上来与我交战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.04,0:17:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看我吕布单枪匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如何连砍你们十八颗脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主 大敌当前 董贼亲至
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此战许胜不许败
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某不才 愿为盟军排兵布阵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄请
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布再是悍勇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不过是一介匹夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.14,0:17:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他之所以敢如此嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是因为董卓的大军距此不远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓是想用吕布为饵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}引我们出关作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与他的西凉军野战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三个时辰之内我们不可出关迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们要等到日过晌午
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军人困马乏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}方可开关迎敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.47,0:18:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得好是好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可袁术答应给我的两万斤粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至今还没有踪影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有粮草
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叫我的兵马饿着肚子奔袭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁公路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你答应拨给我的三千兵马在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有我部的粮草呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么时候发给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍给了你多少粮饷兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为何老替他说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.85,0:18:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是你天皇老子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公孙将军 你欺人太甚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本太守会盟以来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何曾得到过一兵一卒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}韩馥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为何霸占我当阳三郡不还
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好哇 我倒想问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为何纵容部将坏我城池
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}掠夺我部的战马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这笔账我还没跟你算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诸公住口 听我曹某一言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我算是明白天下大乱的根源了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正如玄德所言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下大乱的根源在于人心丧乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓的大军正在关前挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们却在这儿勾心斗角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天下岂能不乱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}众诸侯安静 不要打了 不要打了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}呆徒莽汉 竖子枭雄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不足以论大事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.45,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德兄 留步 请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德 在下就要出城了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}行色匆匆 不及面辞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请阁下恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.26,0:19:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么要走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是觉得袁绍不配做盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是玄德兄无意于功名利禄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍配不配做盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下不敢妄议
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.57,0:20:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我兄弟三个前来会盟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是为了诛贼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并不是为了功名利禄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某也有一句话搁在心里很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请孟德示下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们三兄弟的报国壮志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.76,0:20:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忠义豪情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某极为敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下斗胆相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请你们暂居曹营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们共创大业如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多谢孟德厚爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过我三兄弟刚刚离开袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}转眼就投入曹营
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德不怕众诸侯非议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.46,0:20:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下也斗胆直言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘备别无所长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但为事的原则却恪守不变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过此刻你们也出不了城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为吕布此刻正在关前挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这小子真的来啦 来的好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有句话不知道你们听说过没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个世上有两样绝品
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是谓人中吕布 马中赤兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布手中那杆方天画戟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使得那是出神入化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他胯下的那匹赤兔马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}日行千里 快如闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他还视天下英雄为草芥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}山川巨谷在赤兔马的脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是如履平地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓得吕布胜得十万雄兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今更可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这两样绝品居然合二为一了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此刻吕布正骑着赤兔马
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在关前挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是十八路诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}居然没有一个人敢去应战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全都像缩头乌龟一样地不敢露面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.97,0:22:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我觉得你们也是先回避一下为好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥二哥 你们暂且在这里稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看我捅吕布那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一万个透明窟窿去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟 吕布勇猛过人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是由我来战他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二哥 你先前已经斩了华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如是你要是抢我的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可就不认你这二哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟啊 还是听大哥的吩咐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你瞧你把我两兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都激成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里 我是好意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我觉得我们还是要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:22:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回避一下吕布这头猛虎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:23:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 在下也有一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请曹公转告袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我三兄弟会盟当日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}便送了一份大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为盟军斩了华雄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日我三兄弟离去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.07,0:23:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}同样还要再送盟军一份大礼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.17,0:23:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何礼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.58,0:23:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}斩吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}玄德兄这一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.88,0:23:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足以羞煞十八路诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.36,0:23:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}令你出战吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和你二哥为你掠阵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.59,0:24:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍 你不是四世三公吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.56,0:24:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是盛名满天下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何不敢和我吕布一战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何胆小如鼠 缩首如龟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.57,0:24:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们十八镇诸侯甘做鼠辈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.88,0:24:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三姓家奴 休得猖狂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.99,0:24:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燕人张翼德在此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你叫我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.42,0:24:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三姓家奴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我堂堂吕布 为何成了三姓家奴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.27,0:24:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你小子姓吕是不
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.97,0:24:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.37,0:24:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可你先拜了丁原将军做义父
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.97,0:25:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那董卓用了一匹赤兔马
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.18,0:25:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就把你给收买过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.18,0:25:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你竟然为了一匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.28,0:25:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就亲手杀了你义父丁原
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.58,0:25:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}后来认董卓做了义父
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.79,0:25:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不是三姓家奴是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.69,0:25:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三姓家奴 快来受死 驾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.46,0:25:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三姓家奴 拿命来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.77,0:25:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.87,0:26:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三姓家奴 劲儿还真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.29,0:28:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三姓家奴
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.70,0:30:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.90,0:30:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是个英雄豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.50,0:30:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓是乱世奸贼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.21,0:30:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为何要失身于贼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.81,0:30:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为何不归顺朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.28,0:30:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为大汉建立万世功勋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.18,0:30:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此时我三兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.18,0:30:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要你性命如探囊取物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.38,0:30:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是英雄相惜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.98,0:30:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等不忍杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.88,0:30:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听吾一言 快快弃暗投明
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.49,0:30:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 不必跟他啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.49,0:30:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三姓家奴 看枪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.21,0:31:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥小心
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.31,0:32:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过瘾 不过瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.51,0:32:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他小子怎么跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.61,0:32:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人武艺高强
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.91,0:32:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愧是人间吕布马中赤兔
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.51,0:32:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.48,0:32:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此英雄却陷入奸人之手
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.48,0:32:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 你又动了恻隐之心了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.49,0:32:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人不可教化
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.79,0:32:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大哥 二哥
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.49,0:32:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在正好乘胜追杀才是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.49,0:32:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓大军肯定藏于山后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.80,0:32:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二弟 三弟 不必再追了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.80,0:32:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董贼若在 正好取他首级
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.00,0:32:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀过去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.90,0:32:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三弟 三弟 回来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.10,0:32:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.79,0:33:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁盟主 贼军势穷 良机难得
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.79,0:33:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快传命进军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.19,0:33:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.09,0:33:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}众将听令
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.09,0:33:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大开城门 出战董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.39,0:33:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵令
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.94,0:33:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出战 出战 出战
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.70,0:33:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快 快
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.91,0:33:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹仁
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.61,0:33:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.71,0:33:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我部将士何在
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.31,0:33:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全部集结完毕 都在城东待命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.81,0:33:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 随我直奔虎牢关 攻取洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.42,0:33:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.90,0:33:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨夜老夫得到密报
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.40,0:33:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍率领的王师
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.21,0:33:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经攻破了虎牢关
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.11,0:33:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大获全胜 好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.81,0:33:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军之溃败
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.11,0:34:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓被刘关张三兄弟刺于马下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.02,0:34:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.29,0:34:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好啊 生死不明 那就是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.09,0:34:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上天哪 苍生有幸 日月光复啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.90,0:34:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想西凉军败兵
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.40,0:34:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正在仓惶逃命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.40,0:34:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我王师兵临城下
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.51,0:34:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼瞅着破城在即
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.71,0:34:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我大汉不日即可复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.11,0:34:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我快将这消息
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.51,0:34:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶紧告诉太后和天子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.92,0:34:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们赶紧召集人手
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.62,0:34:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}准备应变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.19,0:34:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好 是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.90,0:34:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒大人 董 董相在宫里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.31,0:35:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国在殿里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.11,0:35:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}天还没亮相国就带着甲士们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.91,0:35:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}闯进皇宫里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.32,0:35:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍的五十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.12,0:35:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被咱家打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.09,0:35:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死伤大部
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.89,0:35:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是还有些部分残余
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.30,0:35:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可能要进犯京城 掠夺圣驾
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.60,0:35:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以咱家是不得不防啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.31,0:35:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 近日有童谣说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.21,0:35:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}东头一个汉 西头一个汉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.11,0:35:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迁都入长安 方可无斯难
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.72,0:35:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 真好 说的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.12,0:35:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}东都洛阳历经二百年
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.49,0:35:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}气数已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.99,0:35:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家是夜观天象
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.60,0:35:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}见帝气旺于长安
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.60,0:36:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 咱家决定奉驾西幸
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.30,0:36:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迁都于长安
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.61,0:36:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么各位百官公卿们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.81,0:36:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都快快准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.01,0:36:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}促装起行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.32,0:36:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀相国
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.22,0:36:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自从黄巾起事之后 连年兵戈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.03,0:36:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早已将长安化为一片断壁残垣
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.70,0:36:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国如果西迁长安
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.90,0:36:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}犹如弃宫室而就瓦砾
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.10,0:36:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万万不妥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.80,0:36:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恳请相国明察
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.11,0:36:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}懂什么国家大计
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.71,0:36:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迁都长安那是中兴大汉王朝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.41,0:36:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是百年大计
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.32,0:36:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}洛阳暗 长安明
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.22,0:36:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迁都长安就是弃暗投明
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.79,0:36:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}启禀相国
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.83,0:37:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}京都洛阳乃朝廷命脉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.10,0:37:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倘若无故离宗庙 弃皇陵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.70,0:37:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将使朝廷大乱 百姓沦难
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.00,0:37:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此关天之事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.10,0:37:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乞盼相国慎之又慎哪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.61,0:37:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慎之又慎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.21,0:37:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家有什么不慎重了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.01,0:37:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那长安有函关之险 陇山之佑
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.42,0:37:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}建宫用的木材砖瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.22,0:37:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它是唾手可得
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.73,0:37:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家半月之内
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.13,0:37:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就可以再造一座皇宫
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.00,0:37:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那可比长乐宫舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.61,0:37:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.61,0:37:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家把这个宫定名为万乐宫
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.81,0:37:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万乐宫
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.52,0:37:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 您骤然迁都
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.12,0:38:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}车马如何筹集
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.82,0:38:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百官如何安置
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.42,0:38:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黎民百姓如何料理啊 相国
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.53,0:38:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家有战车兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.83,0:38:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百官们坐上去不就完了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.10,0:38:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}至于那些城中小民 贱如草芥
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.50,0:38:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爱死爱活
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.10,0:38:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家就管不了那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.91,0:38:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}随他去 随他去
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.91,0:38:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然相国的迁都大计已定
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.11,0:38:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问何日起行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.92,0:38:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.52,0:38:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这才是你应该问的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.83,0:38:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听着
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.33,0:38:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家做事向来是雷厉风行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.43,0:38:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}迁都就在今日
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.00,0:38:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么今日午时初刻起行
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.30,0:38:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西迁
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.11,0:38:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 猛然迁都必使朝纲大乱
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.71,0:39:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这万万不可 万万不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.12,0:39:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这贼子肯定是私通袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.52,0:39:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阻我大计 图谋不轨
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.93,0:39:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你今天必死无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.50,0:39:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位爱卿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.91,0:39:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁还有什么好的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.91,0:39:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶快说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.22,0:39:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我这儿听着呢 说啊 有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.03,0:39:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好 来呀 在
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.13,0:39:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伺候天子起驾
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.13,0:39:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.82,0:40:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国有令
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.22,0:40:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将皇宫 宗庙 帝陵 台阁
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.72,0:40:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全部焚毁
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.33,0:40:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不得给贼兵留下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓西迁长安
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.91,0:40:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}数百年汉都洛阳被焚为灰烬
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.41,0:40:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}豪绅富户籍没入官
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.32,0:40:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宗庙帝陵盗掘殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.41,0:41:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹将军进见主公
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.11,0:41:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们总算来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.01,0:41:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.21,0:41:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.42,0:41:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下盼你们真是望眼欲穿哪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.22,0:41:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍何在 大军何在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.42,0:41:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各镇诸侯何在
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.62,0:41:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.59,0:41:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们在六百里外喝酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.83,0:41:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 董卓劫驾西逃
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.33,0:41:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}洛阳城一片大火
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.83,0:41:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军正在败退
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.03,0:41:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍为何不乘胜追杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.34,0:41:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍担心董卓暗藏伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.14,0:41:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各路诸侯也是你望我 我望你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.51,0:41:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁都不肯率先出兵
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.71,0:41:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了一点兵马 粮草 城池
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.32,0:41:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都快打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.02,0:41:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有我率本部万余精骑
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.42,0:41:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星夜驰援于你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.13,0:42:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们盟主真是坐失良机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.93,0:42:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.33,0:42:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你真是太抬举袁绍了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.23,0:42:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他连这个千载难逢的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.44,0:42:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看都没看出来 谈何坐失
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.04,0:42:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄有何高见
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.84,0:42:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.11,0:42:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼下有一个天大的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.61,0:42:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}摆在你我二人眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.81,0:42:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会盟之初 各路诸侯约定
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.32,0:42:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谁先攻入京城
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.92,0:42:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就启奏圣上封谁为骠骑大将军
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.82,0:42:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}眼下 洛阳空虚 董贼败逃
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.93,0:42:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你我何不兵分两路
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.93,0:42:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一路集中所有的步兵开进洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.03,0:42:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}另一路集中所有的骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.64,0:42:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星夜追杀董贼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.34,0:42:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙将军你愿意去哪一路
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.71,0:42:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我部江东子弟大多是步军
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.72,0:42:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}骑兵还不到三千
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.42,0:43:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而我率领的全部都是精骑
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.92,0:43:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙将军
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.99,0:43:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可否把你的三千骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.73,0:43:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全部交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.43,0:43:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会亲自率领他们
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.23,0:43:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}星夜追杀董贼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.53,0:43:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你率步军开进洛阳
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.64,0:43:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当真
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.64,0:43:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}千真万确
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.35,0:43:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.81,0:43:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真就有劳孟德兄了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.02,0:43:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为国除贼 何分彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.92,0:43:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}文台兄你我何不即刻分头行动
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.32,0:43:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.23,0:43:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}程普
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.43,0:43:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.93,0:43:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把所有骑兵全部交付曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.24,0:43:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.44,0:43:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保重
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.94,0:43:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}珍重
